# Jude shorthand

When the user sends only a number or uses these codes in context:

| Code | Action |
|------|--------|
| **42** | Push to GitHub (`main`) and deploy both apps to Vercel production (`apps/demo` → jude.one, `apps/marketing` → urjude.com). Run `npm run 42` from repo root. |
| **67** | Start or restart local dev. Run `npm run dev:demo` (port 3002, jude.one demo). If the screen is blank after changes, kill the dev server and run 67 again. Marketing site: `npm run dev:marketing` (port 3001). |

## Project layout

- `apps/demo` — jude.one wall-mounted interface demo
- `apps/marketing` — urjude.com marketing & registration landing page

## Product context

Jude is a home AI member of the family — like Jarvis but friendly enough for grandparents. Not Alexa.
